    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey friend! You have to see this car \u2013 it\u2019s honestly a total gem. I've babied it since day one, and it\u2019s still looking and smelling brand new. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection! It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this incredibly smooth ride. Shoot me a message if you want to come fall in love with your new favorite car!",
