    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve kept it garaged and pampered since day one, and it seriously still looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! It drives like an absolute dream and has been treated with so much love. You really have to see it in person to believe how spotless it is. Feel free to shoot me a message with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
