      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This example features the S54B32 inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings throughout. Power is managed by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual and a 3.25:1 limited-slip differential. Every mechanical component, from the rod bearings to the cooling system, has been proactively serviced to ensure peak performance. The exterior finish retains full factory depth, free of imperfections, representing a turn-key investment for the serious enthusiast.",
